{"tid":2313241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美情報總監：中共無道德底線 發展生物士兵","createTime":"2020-12-05T15:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T15:35:39.000Z","uid":294518,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4df83b0e6741b77efc9e99a414799b5d95be89c0","tid":2313241,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T15:15:21.000Z","msg":"情報總監：中共無道德底線 發展生物士兵 <br />\n<br />\n美国国家情报总监约翰&middot;拉特克里夫周四（12月3日）在《华尔街日报》发表评论文章说：&ldquo;美国情报显示，中国（中共）甚至已对中共军人进行人体测试，希望发展生物能力增强的士兵。北京对武力的追求没有道德伦理界限。&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/12/4/n12594736.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F12%2F4%2Fn12594736.htm&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=dd02fe8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/12/4/n12594736.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/china-is-national-security-threat-no-1-11607019599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fchina-is-national-security-threat-no-1-11607019599&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=05bd1caf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/china-is-national-security-threat-no-1-11607019599</a>"},{"pid":"3bc82b30c1692b0256849c4e1e1112c176830bca","tid":2313241,"uid":226955,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T15:17:40.000Z","msg":"一啲都唔意外，蚹蛤蟈蜻"},{"pid":"a894ad7555943d9e49b7cf419b54a53512ff8016","tid":2313241,"uid":294518,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2YBxtfD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2YBxtfD.png&h=09318a44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5487945265e060ab716bc7389862be87ee0b2c1a","tid":2313241,"uid":18001,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T15:18:35.000Z","msg":"BOW<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/a